  "subject": "Add Centos7 docker node",
  "commit_message": "Add Centos7 docker node\n\nCurrently we just had Centos7 builder nodes\nbut with the migration to maven-stage job we will need\nto use Centos7 nodes with docker to allow for some teams\nto run containers as part of their deploy phase.\n\nChange-Id: I330facf5508f44233f2cf4c23a909ffb8045f760\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nSigned-off-by: Jessica Wagantall <jwagantall@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
